&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;[2] Estatuto da Comunidade:&lt;a href="http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/CommunityBylaws" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;br&gt;http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/CommunityBylaws&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;[3] Mais sobre o Comitê de Associados:&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/TDF/Membership_Committee" target="_blank"&gt;http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/TDF/Membership_Committee&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;* fonte: &lt;a href="http://blog.documentfoundation.org/2011/04/19/the-document-foundation-is-open-for-members/" target="_blank"&gt;The Document Foundation blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Apr 2011 10:14:05 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/the-document-foundation-abre-inscricoes-para-membros</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/the-document-foundation-abre-inscricoes-para-membros</guid></item></channel></rss>